<subSubSection id="24CB1080FFAAFFF4FAB2A8068290F80A" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="6C6E430BFFAAFFF4FAB2A8068290F80A" blockId="30.[151,1437,1715,2030]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFAAFFF4FAB2A806815EF866" bold="true" box="[199,315,1896,1922]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previous records from the coast of 
<collectingRegion id="AE158DE9FFAAFFF4F8AFA806832BF865" box="[730,846,1895,1922]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
include Registro city (MZUSP 11443). There were doubts about the wide distribution of this species in the literature, but it has recently been confirmed to be amphi- Atlantic (see 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFAAFFF4FB43A8C1827BF82E" author="Oliveira, C. M. C. A. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Terossi, M." box="[310,542,1967,1994]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" pagination="780 - 794" refId="ref71771" refString="Oliveira, C. M. C. A., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Terossi, M. (2021) Systematics of the shrimp genus Atya (Decapoda, Atyidae) in the light of multigene-based phylogenetic and species delimitation inference. Zoologica Scripta, 50 (6), 780 - 794. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / zsc. 12503" type="journal article" year="2021">
Oliveira 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFAAFFF4FBE8A8DE81B6F82D" box="[413,467,1967,1993]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">et al</emphasis>
. 2021
</bibRefCitation>
for review). Sequences accession number (GenBank): MZUSP 11443—16S (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FFAAFFF4FAD5A8BD8147F80A" box="[160,290,2003,2030]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/KY582529" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">KY582529</accessionNumber>
), COI (
<accessionNumber id="7382DEE8FFAAFFF4FB00A8BD8196F80A" box="[373,499,2003,2030]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/KY582538" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">KY582538</accessionNumber>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFAAFFF4F87CA8BD828CF80A" author="Oliveira, C. M. C. A. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Terossi, M." box="[521,745,2003,2030]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" pagination="780 - 794" refId="ref71771" refString="Oliveira, C. M. C. A., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Terossi, M. (2021) Systematics of the shrimp genus Atya (Decapoda, Atyidae) in the light of multigene-based phylogenetic and species delimitation inference. Zoologica Scripta, 50 (6), 780 - 794. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / zsc. 12503" type="journal article" year="2021">
Oliveira 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFAAFFF4F81BA8BA82FAF809" box="[622,671,2003,2029]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">et al</emphasis>
